uences range from ~\n4.4\\times10^{-9} ergs/cm^-2 to ~ 2.7\\times10^{-6} ergs/cm^{-2}, consistent with\nthose observed for typical short SGR bursts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Apr 2010 01:35:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-18"}
